[[image me.png]]

[[collapsible show="+ What is this?" hide="- Hide explanation"]]
[[div class="body-text"]]
**How it works:** Some folks entered their characters into a contest.

I want in.

I'm gonna force 'em to take me.
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]

[[collapsible show="+ What are the rules?" hide="- Hide rules."]]
[[div class="body-text"]]

**Notes on termination:** 
* I will remember you.
* I will commit mass murders if necessary.
* I will not stop until I kill you.

**Tips:**
* Running is pointless.
* Hiding is pointless.
* Make peace with your death.

**More rules:**
* I'll get you when I get to you.
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]
